OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA warm
OL,6,Fevening with plenty of late sunshine.
OL,7,FStaying largely dry overnight with
OL,8,Fclear periods although patchy low
OL,9,Fcloud may develop, with a chance of
OL,10,Fisolated fog patches. Staying rather
OL,11,Fwarm in some urban areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAny mist rapidly clearing,
OL,14,Fthen a mostly sunny day with wispy
OL,15,Fhigh cloud at times. Fair weather
OL,16,Fcloud developing into the afternoon
OL,17,Fbut lengthy sunny periods continuing.
OL,18,FBecoming very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
